## Running locally

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

## Building for production

```bash
npm run build
npm run preview
```

Output goes to `dist/`. Deploy the contents of `dist/` to GitHub Pages.

## Updating content

All text, projects, skills, services, and contact info live in `src/data/content.json`. Edit that file â€” no component changes needed.



























